 - Lightweight Threads, Channels, Actors for JVM -
 
 - How Light Wt ?
 -----------------------
 - Coz they are not scheduled by OS
 - Hence, they require far less system resources
 - Hence, their Context Switch is often faster
 - So, can we say a single machine can handle millions of them
 
 
 
